This is a validation study.

 A stroke symptom questionnaire will be adapted and translated into local language.

 Two community health workers will be trained in its administration.

 Their findings will be validated against assessment by two neurologists.

 The study hypothesis is that the chance corrected agreement between the community worker administered stroke symptom questionnaire and the assessment by neurologist based on history and physical examination is at least moderate.

